data.description: This two-story condo possesses lots of natural light, vaulted ceilings and a two-sided gas fireplace, for those chilly Colorado days. A rare corner unit spacious condo with an open main floor living and kitchen area. A separate laundry room with included washer and dryer and a powder room complete the main floor. On the second floor you will find the primary bedroom and private bathroom, a walk in closet and the second ensuite bedroom/bathroom combo. This condo has easy access to the pool (maintained by the HOA), visitor parking, detached garage spot and deeded parking space right out the front door. There is plenty of storage throughout the condo. Located only 10 minutes to Cherry Creek Plaza and 20 minutes to Downtown Denver in a highly sought after Cherry Creek School district. This home is a must see in a desirable neighborhood, unit may be used as an income property. Welcome home!
